name: TopStories-India
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, what's in the news?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
This Skill fetches the latest news for India, updates are for Top News, Technology & Sports.
By default only the Top News feed is enabled. Make sure to enable the Technology & Sports feed under Settings -> Flash Briefing -> Scroll down to 'off' section -> enable 
Updated hourly. Depending on new content availability.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
